            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "__GHOST_URL__/vehicles/110990/1961-dodge-jeep-mighty-mite",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is up for sale through the Orlando Auto Museum. Details on the vehicle itself are scarce, but from the supplied picture documentation, the Mighty Mite could use a little cosmetic TLC. It appears as though the canvas hood may need replacing and – as a museum piece – the mechanicals will most likely require a full-on service. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "type": "linebreak",
